faq.question: How much does it cost to use ChatGPT?
faq.answer: ChatGPT offers both free and subscription-based plans. The subscription plans provide enhanced features and usage limits.

faq.question: How does ChatGPT work?
faq.answer: ChatGPT uses a deep learning model called GPT-4. It processes text input and generates human-like responses based on the input it receives.

faq.question: Why does the AI seem so real and lifelike?
faq.answer: The AI seems real and lifelike due to the advanced natural language processing algorithms and the extensive training data it has been exposed to.

faq.question: Can I trust that the AI is telling me the truth?
faq.answer: While the AI strives to provide accurate and helpful information, it may not always be correct. It's important to verify critical information from reliable sources.

faq.question: Who can view my conversations?
faq.answer: Your conversations are confidential and can only be accessed by authorized personnel to improve the service or if required by law.

faq.question: Why does the AI seem so real and lifelike?
faq.answer: The AI seems real and lifelike due to the advanced natural language processing algorithms and the extensive training data it has been exposed to.

faq.question: Can I trust that the AI is telling me the truth?
faq.answer: While the AI strives to provide accurate and helpful information, it may not always be correct. It's important to verify critical information from reliable sources.

faq.question: Who can view my conversations?
faq.answer: Your conversations are confidential and can only be accessed by authorized personnel to improve the service or if required by law.
